data.title: Long-term detailed weather forecast for the city of Sant'Antonio di Gallura with a time resolution of three hours

data.text:
night0:00+22 °CClear

Wind: light breeze, southern

speed: 7 km/h

On land:

Wind felt on face; leaves rustle; ordinary vanes moved by wind.

At Sea:

Small wavelets, still short, but more pronounced. Crests have a glassy appearance and do not break.

Wind gusts: 11 km/h

Atmospheric pressure: 975 hPa

Relative humidity: 91%

Cloudiness: 7%

State of the sea: calm (rippled)

wave height of: 0,2 m

Visibility: 100%

Wind: light air, southern

speed: 4 km/h

Direction of wind shown by smoke drift, but not by wind vanes.

Ripples with the appearance of scales are formed, but without foam crests.
